[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "beginner"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/basic_notrump"]
[Student "S"]
{This is an easy one to bid.

WEST has a balanced 16 points so he opens 1NT.

EAST has a balanced 12 points so she responds 3NT.

BUT - just look at how this would play. You might only be able to take 8 tricks. 
Sometimes correct bidding gets you to unmakeable contracts. But it's only a game.}

